DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

95-2126. Disciplinary Counsel v. Marshall.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that David Steele Marshall, Attorney Registration No. 0031544, last known address in Mentor, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of February 28,1996, to wit, failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before March 29,1996.
